@startuml
title Detection and Recording

participant "Perception Service" as Perception
participant "Control Plane API" as API
participant "Stream Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Recording Worker" as Recorder
participant YOLO
database "Metadata Store" as Metadata
database "Media Store" as Media

API -> Perception: Publish desired camera config snapshot
loop Per configured camera
  Perception -> Gateway: Consume normalized stream feed
  Gateway --> Perception: Frames or stream tap
  Perception -> Perception: Fuse motion signals and evaluate trigger policy

  alt Trigger conditions met
    Perception -> YOLO: Classify frame
    YOLO --> Perception: Labels and confidence
    Perception -> API: Publish ObservationEvent
    API -> Metadata: Store observation
    Perception -> Recorder: Emit RecordingIntent
    Recorder -> Gateway: Pull or subscribe to recording source
    Recorder -> Media: Write clip and thumbnail
    Recorder -> API: Publish RecordingCompleted
    API -> Metadata: Store recording catalog rows
  end
end

@enduml
